      "duration": 14.604664723032071,
      "emotion": "thinking",
      "endTime": 58.418658892128285,
      "environment": "A sunny path in the forest",
      "narrationText": "कुछ दिनों बाद, एक छोटे से खरगोश की बारी आई। खरगोश बहुत बुद्धिमान था। उसने अपनी जान बचाने के लिए एक योजना बनाई।",
      "sceneIndex": 3,
      "startTime": 43.81399416909621,
      "visualPrompt": "Small white rabbit walking slowly on a forest path, lightbulb moment expression."
    },
    {
      "action": "Sher Singh roaring at the tiny rabbit who is standing calmly in front of him.",
      "beatTitle": "The Angry Lion",
      "characters": [
        "Sher Singh",
